    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/c22edd5eb7a8e44390b509f5b7f50d1e.avif?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/2bf114ae3056f9590899894e42681343.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>邪气经典韩国恐怖游戏回归</strong> -《White Day VR:The Courage Test》是沉浸式的 VR 体验，让玩家们在死亡之夜中回到 Yeondu High School，接受一段与众不同的战栗挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/277e3d7880cc30f932350ba2ec6a3143.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>试胆</strong> - 为了进入 Occult Club，学生们必须接受“试胆”。当 Occult Club 的老成员 Da-Hee Kim 告诉你测试提前一天的时候，你又如何知道，她是否可以信任？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/5e6e8b7038376f9f546cc68cac1931e9.avif?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/7a5b36800ee8567179181aa29a4dc68e.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>踏入 1-1 教室</strong> - 因原因不明的事故，1-1 教室早已被关闭，现在它被用作储藏室。踏入怪异黑暗，使用 VR 控制器与其中腐朽的家具互动，找出 15 件隐藏的物品。   <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/cfbf8d996693d97f676c15ae51889a26.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>限时试胆</strong> - 挑战者仅有 5 分钟去寻找所有物品，而在黑暗中你会发现的，绝不仅仅只有旧家具和隐藏的物品而已...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/2dcda8698d1afb56723f4a70dc3d4fdd.avif?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/897d4634373b4386add59c40a1108747.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>多种结局</strong> - 试胆以往只有两种结局：成功或者失败。你又会发现何种结局呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/dd6e840fbf2cfb161d9462ee7520543e.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>借助 Unreal Engine 创作的令人战栗画面</strong> - 在这个高质量 VR 体验中，以惊人的细节体验夜间学校的恐怖。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/d90bc8cf36119c92182d1edab7ce7c69.avif?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/078abeb1cbc6cd200b010e40b2e97589.webp?t=1741787367\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><strong>沉浸 3D 音效</strong> - 清晰的三维音效，令脚步、地板门扇嘎吱声和怪异声响清晰可辩。",
